name: All The Hidden Quanta - Postcard from Leslie Road, Essendon - Headset phone call - 2022/01/10
description: The "All the Hidden Quanta - Postcard from ..." series using Processing visual arts language, explores the concept that we are surrounded by the unseen (unacknowledged? unrealised?), constantly in flux world of quanta. This project was processed from real time camera captures whilst making a headset phone call (Sharon's in the background). mp4, 1280x960px, 25fps, 50seconds(please loop), 90.5MB.
